main event: A witness observed a large round disc with two objects circling around it for approximately 30 seconds in Renton, Washington.
interesting points: The disc was bright blue and red in color., The witness ran inside the house as the objects left at a high rate of speed., The objects descended to about 25 feet off the ground., The sighting occurred at night with clear weather conditions., The witness noted that there was no sound emitted from the disc.
sighted object: a large round disc with two circling objects
witness description: the observer was putting the family cat outside when the sighting occurred
